# Project Overview

This is a personal portfolio website for Damien Villeneuve, a full-stack product engineer based in Nantes, France.

## Tech Stack
- Built with [Vite](mdc:vite.config.ts), [React 18](mdc:src/main.tsx), and [TypeScript](mdc:tsconfig.json)
- Styling with [Tailwind CSS](mdc:tailwind.config.js)
- Animations with Framer Motion
- Carousels with Swiper.js
- SEO optimization with React Helmet Async
- Routing with React Router v6
- Internationalization with i18next

## Key Entry Points
- [main.tsx](mdc:src/main.tsx) - Application entry point
- [App.tsx](mdc:src/App.tsx) - Main application component
- [index.css](mdc:src/index.css) - Global CSS styles

## Project Structure
- `/src/components` - React components
- `/src/pages` - Application pages
- `/src/data` - Data files (projects, social links)
- `/src/assets` - Static assets
- `/src/hooks` - Custom React hooks
- `/src/locales` - Internationalization files
